  "name": "First-Order Passive RC High-Pass Filter",
  "description": "Reusable first-order passive RC high-pass filter block for a 1 V AC input, with output taken across the shunt resistor. The nominal component values of 10 kOhm and 10 nF yield a cutoff frequency of approximately 1.59 kHz and satisfy the stated magnitude limits at 100 Hz and 10 kHz when driving a high-impedance load.",
